data.description: This stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bath home boasts a welcoming open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, creating an atmosphere of spaciousness and grandeur. Hardwood flooring graces the living and dining rooms, adding a touch of elegance and durability. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, blending modernity with functionality. A cozy fireplace in the family room provides warmth and a charming focal point. On the first floor, you'll find a convenient bedroom, a full bath, and a laundry area. Upstairs, a versatile loft space awaits, perfect for a home office or additional living area. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, offering a generous layout, an en suite bathroom for added privacy, and a walk-in closet providing ample storage. Outside, a spacious backyard, adorned with mature trees, offers an inviting setting for entertaining or simply enjoying the beauty of nature. This home seamlessly combines comfort, style, and practicality, creating a space that you'll be excited to call your own.
